you're picking yourself up,

01:20:29.710 --> 01:20:33.660
recognize that this new
situation with the economy

01:20:33.660 --> 01:20:37.100
that doesn't have the juice
to sustain our institutions,

01:20:37.100 --> 01:20:39.730
has caused the people
who've risen to the top

01:20:39.730 --> 01:20:43.420
of those institutions to
get quite brutal and cruel.

01:20:43.420 --> 01:20:45.130
